'''2013年环西自行车赛'''是第68届[[环西自行车赛|环西自行车赛]]，于2013年8月24日至9月15日进行，此次比赛是2013年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛<ref name="BBC News">{{cite web|url=http://velonews.competitor.com/2012/11/news/spanish-rumor-mill-hints-at-a-2013-vuelta-a-espana-thats-even-hillier-than-12-edition_265570|title=Spanish rumor mill hints at a 2013 Vuelta a España that's even hillier than '12 edition|date=2012-11-18|accessdate=2012-11-18|work=VeloNews|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233102/http://velonews.competitor.com/2012/11/news/spanish-rumor-mill-hints-at-a-2013-vuelta-a-espana-thats-even-hillier-than-12-edition_265570|archivedate=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。比赛共分为21个赛段，起点位于[[加利西亚_(西班牙)|加利西亚]]，终点位于[[马德里|马德里]]，除第十四赛段途经[[安道尔|安道尔]]，第十五赛段在安道尔和[[法国|法国]]进行外，其余比赛路线均在西班牙境内<ref name="TdF_A">{{cite web|url=http://velonews.competitor.com/2013/01/vuelta-a-espana/hints-on-vuelta-route-more-mountainous-than-2012-edition_270349|title=Hints on Vuelta route: More mountainous than 2012 edition|work=VeloNews|date=2013-01-02|accessdate=2013-01-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305230306/http://velonews.competitor.com/2013/01/vuelta-a-espana/hints-on-vuelta-route-more-mountainous-than-2012-edition_270349|archivedate=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

共有22支车队参加此次比赛，其中19支车队为世界职业车队，另外3支车队则为洲际职业车队<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.velonation.com/News/ID/14491/Caja-Rural-Cofidis-and-NetApp-Endura-awarded-Vuelta-a-Espana-wildcards.aspx|title=Caja Rural, Cofidis and NetApp-Endura awarded Vuelta a España wildcards|work=VeloNation|date=2013-05-03|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524043758/http://www.velonation.com/News/ID/14491/Caja-Rural-Cofidis-and-NetApp-Endura-awarded-Vuelta-a-Espana-wildcards.aspx|archivedate=2013-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终来自无线电-猎豹车队的美国选手[[Chris_Horner|Chris Horner]]获得该届比赛的总冠军，以41岁的年龄成为历史上年龄最大的[[三大自行车环赛|三大自行车环赛]]总冠军<ref name="Horner">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/cycling/24101494|title=Vuelta a Espana:  Chris Horner, 41, is oldest Grand Tour winner|date=2013-09-15|work=[[BBC体育|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2013-09-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917072727/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/cycling/24101494|archivedate=2013-09-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2013/sep/15/vuelta-a-espana-christopher-horner|title=Christopher Horner becomes oldest grand tour champion|date=2013-09-15|work=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|accessdate=2013-09-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917143841/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2013/sep/15/vuelta-a-espana-christopher-horner|archivedate=2013-09-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/sports/endurance/story/_/id/9677342/christopher-horner-us-wins-spanish-vuelta-oldest-grand-tour-champion|title=Chris Horner wins Spanish Vuelta|date=2013-09-15|work=ESPN|accessdate=2013-09-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130916224806/http://espn.go.com/sports/endurance/story/_/id/9677342/christopher-horner-us-wins-spanish-vuelta-oldest-grand-tour-champion|archivedate=2013-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。来自阿斯塔纳车队的意大利选手[[溫琴佐·尼巴利|溫琴佐·尼巴利]]和来自移动之星车队的西班牙选手[[Alejandro_Valverde|Alejandro Valverde]]分别获得第二和第三，其中Valverde还获得象征冲刺积分第一的绿衫。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/cycling/2013/09/15/christopher-horner-wins-spanish-vuelta-oldest-grand-tour-champion/2816175/|title=Christopher Horner wins Vuelta as oldest grand tour champion|date=2013-09-15|work=USA Today|accessdate=2013-09-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130915181516/http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/cycling/2013/09/15/christopher-horner-wins-spanish-vuelta-oldest-grand-tour-champion/2816175/|archivedate=2013-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cyclingweekly.co.uk/news/latest/540389/chris-horner-wins-2013-vuelta-a-espana.html|title=Chris Horner wins 2013 Vuelta a Espana|date=2013-09-15|work=Cycling Weekly|accessdate=2013-09-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918061942/http://www.cyclingweekly.co.uk/news/latest/540389/chris-horner-wins-2013-vuelta-a-espana.html|archivedate=2013-09-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>

